畫室的兼職工作，但必須從今日起隔離14日，她打算請假。她與3名子女同住，擔心家居隔離時會令他們受感染，她說「其實我寧願搬入隔離營」。<br />\n<br />\n港人阮先生和妻子上月到廣東新會探親，兩夫婦表示，未來14日依靠居於附近的兒子和媳婦幫忙買菜。法例規定，違反強制檢疫者，一經定罪最高罰款2.5萬元及監禁6個月，阮先生認為具阻嚇力。<br />\n<br />\n不願透露姓名、持雙程證入境的內地八旬婆婆指出，她持有「3個月多次」的探親簽注，從上海來香港照顧患病的姊姊。她表示會尊重香港的防疫政策留在家中。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200208/s00001/1581143011677/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200208%2Fs00001%2F1581143011677%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=321e497d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200208%2Fs00001%2F1581143011677%2F&h=66f90b82\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200208/s00001/1581143011677/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:40:36.000Z","msg":"逗留十分鐘夠瀨嘢了."},{"pid":"0050aed2ea2952ead1237fa265256bf18f32eebc","tid":1869363,"uid":274756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82055cc97edba2adb9caca5e336edd4d9bece4de","tid":1869363,"uid":259813,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f12bcb52c9df4584e87ad7e07774befd5f8f66a","tid":1869363,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"402de9e571726ddc14a6a4841f48e0b9ed7fc595","tid":1869363,"uid":3860,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"真係反社會到極點<br />\n為左唔認衰連呢d 位都唔用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"望佢快啲中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢鬥氣唔戴口罩 中咗就變播毒者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:54:04.000Z","msg":"響政總播哂俾班鳩官<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8799e68fbd2696f7e40bd2f446f575d